@node 1 " Chapter 1. Introduction"
In Norway, we have two TV-stations, which have Teletext
with the possibility to send in your own advertisements via Phone.
StttttS emulates the phonesounds and sends it through a cable
you buy very cheap from me. The cable can be connected between any
amiga and most telephones.

StttttS is made especially to log adverts into teletextstations 
in a fast and simple way. The program is fast, easy to use and
has lots of possibilities.

This is an Amos program, and that means that you can multitask
just by pressing the left amiga + a.

StttttS means: Snyt Tv To's Tekst Tv Tjeneste Skikkelig. or:
	       Cheat Tv channels Teletext advertisement
	       service Real.
@endnode


